sequenceDiagram
  participant Apps as apps.Order
  participant Fulfillment as fulfillment.Order
  participant Processing as processing.Order
  participant Inventory as Inventory / Allocations
  participant Agent as ShippingAgent
  participant Carrier as Carrier / Shipping

  Apps->>Fulfillment: validateOrder Nexus operation<br/>UpdateWithStart
  Fulfillment->>Fulfillment: verify address
  Fulfillment->>Inventory: holdItems

  par Processing path
    Apps->>Processing: processOrder Nexus operation
    Processing-->>Apps: ProcessedOrder
  and Fulfillment path
    Fulfillment->>Fulfillment: wait for fulfillOrder Update
  end

  Apps->>Fulfillment: fulfillOrder Update<br/>ProcessedOrder
  Fulfillment->>Inventory: reserveItems
  Fulfillment->>Agent: recommendShippingOption Nexus operation
  Agent-->>Fulfillment: ShippingRecommendation + options
  Fulfillment->>Fulfillment: apply business decision<br/>set margin/SLA attributes

  par Terminal fulfillment work
    Fulfillment->>Carrier: printShippingLabel
  and
    Fulfillment->>Inventory: deductInventory
  end

  Fulfillment->>Fulfillment: wait for notifyDeliveryStatus Signal

